{"tid":2254951,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"★Nokia 225 4G及 Nokia 215 4G香港上市","createTime":"2020-10-23T07:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T15:21:47.000Z","uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"0f37c9fc6e94149da91991af105a73dcfafee5d0","tid":2254951,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:51:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/234432334.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F234432334.jpg&h=c2c6abf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要說現在最火爆的 4G 功能機是哪部？ Nokia 220 4G 當仁不讓，其在今年4月底上市，穩占「同價位」銷量第一，不過香港沒賣。而這部最火的 4G 功能機也終於迎來了繼任者，全新的 Nokia 225 4G 今天香港正式開賣，定價 HK$498，作為備用機來用非常不錯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNokia 225 4G 其實是一款九宮格實體按鍵功能機，除了支援 4G 網絡和 VoLTE 高清語音外，它還支援 4G 雙卡雙待。 Nokia 表示，Nokia 225 4G 搭載新一代低功耗處理器，速度提升，功耗降低。採用 2.4吋屏幕，最多可以使用一張 32GB 的存儲卡，支援無線外放收音機、強光手電筒等功能，還預裝了經典的《貪食蛇》遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其小巧到可單手舒服把玩的機身加上經典的聚碳酸酯物料，手感那是沒得說，90g 的它就像一個小巧的遙控器。可惜香港只提供黑色選購。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2020/10/22/nokia-225-and-nokia-215-hk-released/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2020%2F10%2F22%2Fnokia-225-and-nokia-215-hk-released%2F&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRMVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=a68b2a15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2020/10/22/nokia-225-and-nokia-215-hk-released/</a>"},{"pid":"cc2ad185cae724e4d1a73429d94d54704a6529ba","tid":2254951,"uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:51:28.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><del>iphone 12</del></span>"},{"pid":"6ad84f43f39bc86659d82d7dfc5ad631d269711c","tid":2254951,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:51:54.000Z","msg":"今次 HMD 除了把 Nokia 225 4G 帶來香港，還有一部 Nokia 215 4G，機身設計比 Nokia 225 4G 更為圓潤及厚身。支援 VoLTE 高清語音 及 4G 雙卡雙待，無需插耳機的 FM 收音機亦是經典機最愛。還有20年前驚人的超特大 2.4吋屏幕，8鍵快速撥號，不過就沒有鏡頭。<br />\n<br />\nNokia 215 4G 定價 HK$398，亦都是只有黑色。<br />\n<br />\n以上兩款機都已經在香港上市，想買可以去睇睇。"},{"pid":"bd86b6956fa88740f03c39b85fb5d2594b8ec84f","tid":2254951,"uid":19454,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:52:24.000Z","msg":"無需插耳機的 FM 收音機<br />\n無需插耳機的 FM 收音機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a1636e48247bb3726d011a6a0563a8dec252072","tid":2254951,"uid":156652,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:52:45.000Z","msg":"呢d電話，係好用，一野就打得出"},{"pid":"35b4dd204d98334c2d9602d210c90b0915e6441a","tid":2254951,"uid":2373,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"bd86b6956fa88740f03c39b85fb5d2594b8ec84f","tid":2254951,"uid":19454,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:52:24.000Z","msg":"無需插耳機的 FM 收音機<br />\n無需插耳機的 FM 收音機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:56:23.000Z","msg":"呢個真係正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b474366a8c9e17bb9949abdeadbff5e4ccf3a4a","tid":2254951,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35b4dd204d98334c2d9602d210c90b0915e6441a","tid":2254951,"uid":2373,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"bd86b6956fa88740f03c39b85fb5d2594b8ec84f","tid":2254951,"uid":19454,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:52:24.000Z","msg":"無需插耳機的 FM 收音機<br />\n無需插耳機的 FM 收音機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet